--------------------Table <table> -------------------------
<table></table> -> create the table
<td></td> -> a cell that contains data*
<tr></tr> -> table rows (ligne)

<thead></thead> -> Indicate the head of the table
<tbody></tbody> -> Indicate the body of the table
<tfooter></tfooter> -> Indicate the bottom of the table

rowspan -> taille en ligne de la cellule <td rowspan = "2">
colspan -> taille en colone de la cellule <td rowspan = "2">

--------------------Forms <form> -------------------------
(formulaire)
Containers for a collection of Inputs and send it.
action : where it is send <form action ="">
method : how the information are send <form method="">
hit enter to send the form

check MDN for all input
<input> : can be 20+ different types
    change the attribute type.
    type : text, password, color , numbers, checkbox, radiobutton, select, range, 
    name : name to refering the value of the input
    placeholder : a placeholder value, will be removed when typing
<label></label> : 
    <label for="cheese"> Do you like cheese ? </label>
    <input type = "checkbox" id="cheese">
    id have to be UNIQUE ! 

<button></button> : if a button is inside a form, it by default submit the form.
    type : button, submit (<button type="button"></button>

<textarea></textarea>

Form Validation :
attribut requiered : obligate the input to be filled
attribut minlength/maxlength : require a minimum/maximum length for the name
attribut min/max : minimum/maximum value
attribut pattern : specify the input has to respect the regular expression





